  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PLOT</h2>Phoebus and Venus have met each other an old time ago. For a long time, in the heart of Phoebus, he has always loved Venus, but they have not seen each other for a long time. By chance, they met, and Phoebus finally expressed his love to Venus. But Venus said to Phoebus: \"I can only come back if you find your true love.\" Thus, Phoebus…<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >INSTRUCTION</h2>This game has an excellent interface and model design. You will constantly encounter new obstacles and the map will increase in size with each level. The game also has different hidden endings to wait for you to discover. You can buy equipments in the store, as well as use exceptional functions to reduce the difficulty of the game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MESSAGE</h2>Start your journey now!",
